      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a reliable option for those looking for a practical, budget-friendly car. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches and some minor dings, and the interior exhibits typical wear, including some fading on the upholstery. Mechanically, it remains dependable and has been regularly serviced to ensure it stays roadworthy. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that\u2019s ready for its next owner to put it to good use.",
