    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in superlative condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, remains in an impeccable state. This is an uncompromising example for the discerning collector who demands excellence and absolute mechanical integrity.",
